WEBVTT

00:00:07.725 --> 00:00:11.711
ظآزI found a faint light
in the fading duskظآز

00:00:11.712 --> 00:00:15.311
ظآزAnd met your steady gazeظآز

00:00:15.312 --> 00:00:24.132
ظآزOne knowing glance,
and side by side we walk onظآز

00:00:24.575 --> 00:00:27.061
ظآزLonging finds no place to restظآز

00:00:27.062 --> 00:00:29.211
ظآزThrough drifting wind and rainظآز

00:00:29.212 --> 00:00:32.699
ظآزYou are the prayer within my handsظآز

00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:40.324
ظآزA single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knowsظآز

00:00:40.325 --> 00:00:42.786
ظآزWe made a promise long agoظآز

00:00:42.787 --> 00:00:44.786
ظآزFor all our days to comeظآز

00:00:44.787 --> 00:00:48.449
ظآزYou are the fate I cannot outrunظآز

00:00:48.450 --> 00:00:53.836
ظآزHow much must I let go
to trade for one moment?ظآز

00:00:53.837 --> 00:00:56.457
ظآزHolding you closeظآز

00:00:56.637 --> 00:00:58.874
ظآزWould that be enough?ظآز

00:00:58.875 --> 00:00:59.499
=Echoes of Love=

00:00:59.500 --> 00:01:01.499
(Adapted from the signed screenplay
Echoes of Love on Migu Reading)

00:01:01.500 --> 00:01:03.645
=Episode 19=

00:01:04.037 --> 00:01:06.500
Sir, please make an exception.

00:01:06.779 --> 00:01:08.745
My brother is to be executed tomorrow.

00:01:08.979 --> 00:01:10.220
Let his wife

00:01:10.460 --> 00:01:12.700
see him one last time.

00:01:16.419 --> 00:01:17.980
Go on. Be quick.

00:01:18.900 --> 00:01:21.459
Thank you.

00:01:25.259 --> 00:01:26.659
How tragic.

00:01:32.699 --> 00:01:35.060
(Master Zhou, take my advice.)

00:01:35.540 --> 00:01:37.819
(Drink it now
and spare yourself more pain.)

00:01:37.940 --> 00:01:39.420
(To give your life
for the Shengtang Guild)

00:01:39.580 --> 00:01:41.260
(is the best end you could hope for.)

00:01:53.540 --> 00:01:55.060
I never thought

00:01:56.499 --> 00:01:58.620
the one to see me off

00:01:59.339 --> 00:02:00.860
would be you.

00:02:03.339 --> 00:02:04.500
Zhou Zihua,

00:02:04.900 --> 00:02:06.019
I know

00:02:06.180 --> 00:02:07.140
you must have

00:02:07.419 --> 00:02:09.620
evidence that can bring Madam Ruyi down.

00:02:11.379 --> 00:02:13.259
What you have long wished for,

00:02:13.400 --> 00:02:15.099
I can help you achieve.

00:02:25.980 --> 00:02:27.419
Zhiyun,

00:02:29.140 --> 00:02:30.460
thank you

00:02:32.779 --> 00:02:35.220
for coming to paint
my face one last time.

00:03:47.900 --> 00:03:52.020
Forced before the mirror
to set the hair in place,

00:03:52.580 --> 00:03:56.740
powder brushed on
to conceal the traces of tears.

00:03:59.140 --> 00:04:02.979
(Jade Grove and Fair Trees)
Sorrow swells like rising spring waters,

00:04:03.659 --> 00:04:06.419
my heart, like autumn lotus,

00:04:07.900 --> 00:04:10.460
bitter beyond measure.

00:04:13.387 --> 00:04:17.179
Flawless jade becomes
a target of gossip.

00:04:18.650 --> 00:04:20.778
A beauty fated to suffer...

00:04:20.779 --> 00:04:22.819
Branded as immoral.

00:04:22.820 --> 00:04:24.658
As though born that way.

00:04:24.659 --> 00:04:27.099
She should have
been dealt with long ago.

00:04:28.419 --> 00:04:29.580
Stand aside.

00:04:32.700 --> 00:04:34.020
Disperse.

00:04:50.219 --> 00:04:53.460
Such sorrow, such bitterness.

00:04:55.539 --> 00:04:57.619
(Jade Grove and Fair Trees)
A fair brow and delicate grace,

00:04:59.912 --> 00:05:05.940
yet they bring ruin upon her.

00:05:11.380 --> 00:05:12.820
Three years,

00:05:14.020 --> 00:05:16.419
and you still have not let go.

00:05:22.380 --> 00:05:23.819
They all say

00:05:23.820 --> 00:05:26.220
you are a loyal hound I raised.

00:05:26.739 --> 00:05:28.179
But I

00:05:28.380 --> 00:05:30.659
have never truly mastered you.

00:05:32.140 --> 00:05:34.099
Why must you insist on leaving?

00:05:34.779 --> 00:05:36.659
Once you step out that door,

00:05:37.140 --> 00:05:39.380
I can no longer shield you.

00:05:40.820 --> 00:05:42.020
Stay.

00:05:45.620 --> 00:05:47.020
Shield me?

00:05:49.099 --> 00:05:52.099
You disgust me more
than those who harmed me.

00:05:53.500 --> 00:05:54.619
Zhou Zihua,

00:05:55.779 --> 00:05:57.940
I am not as pitiful as you.

00:05:58.219 --> 00:06:00.220
I have never sought to save myself.

00:06:01.099 --> 00:06:03.419
I only want those who do wrong

00:06:03.500 --> 00:06:05.700
to face the price of it.

00:06:12.099 --> 00:06:12.899
Either

00:06:12.900 --> 00:06:15.739
you let me go, or

00:06:18.700 --> 00:06:20.499
I take your life.

00:06:43.487 --> 00:06:44.886
Take care.

00:07:12.380 --> 00:07:13.780
Take care.

00:07:15.940 --> 00:07:17.059
Zhou Zihua.

00:07:19.620 --> 00:07:22.499
The real jade ruyi is hidden

00:07:25.487 --> 00:07:27.970
in the most obvious place.

00:07:47.450 --> 00:07:51.386
ظآزEven if I drift
within a darkened whirlظآز

00:07:51.387 --> 00:07:54.886
ظآزKindred souls
meet the light and become oneظآز

00:07:54.887 --> 00:08:02.320
ظآزSo many chapters,
every wound rememberedظآز

00:08:02.812 --> 00:08:06.761
ظآزBack where we once stood,
the blossoms still remainظآز

00:08:06.762 --> 00:08:10.295
ظآزThe night runs deep like watching eyesظآز

00:08:11.620 --> 00:08:12.380
Sir,

00:08:12.659 --> 00:08:14.820
everything has been
carried out as ordered.

00:08:15.020 --> 00:08:17.419
Zhou Zihua has taken his own life.

00:08:24.140 --> 00:08:25.460
What is this?

00:08:25.539 --> 00:08:27.619
Who dressed him like this?

00:08:28.020 --> 00:08:30.179
I do not know, sir.

00:08:40.412 --> 00:08:42.012
At this point,

00:08:42.237 --> 00:08:44.699
the only one who dared
oppose the Shengtang Guild

00:08:44.700 --> 00:08:47.020
and still walks free

00:08:47.299 --> 00:08:49.580
must be...

00:08:51.419 --> 00:08:53.820
Mercy, sir. Mercy.

00:08:53.980 --> 00:08:55.219
I was tempted by money.

00:08:55.220 --> 00:08:56.658
A young lady did come

00:08:56.659 --> 00:08:57.820
to see him.

00:08:58.579 --> 00:09:00.979
What did they say?

00:09:01.100 --> 00:09:02.099
I...

00:09:02.220 --> 00:09:03.938
I only heard something about

00:09:03.939 --> 00:09:04.859
ruyi.

00:09:21.550 --> 00:09:24.357
(Huanyue House)

00:09:26.299 --> 00:09:27.700
(The jade ruyi)

00:09:28.059 --> 00:09:29.619
(is hidden)

00:09:29.819 --> 00:09:32.220
(Huanyue House)
(in the most obvious place.)